Manual compound assignment.

```rust
// BAD
x = x + 1;
x = x * 2;

// GOOD
x += 1;
x *= 2;
```

## bool_assert_comparison

Assert with bool comparison.

```rust
// BAD
assert_eq!(result, true);
assert_eq!(result, false);

// GOOD
assert!(result);
assert!(!result);
```

## blocks_in_conditions

Complex blocks in if conditions.

```rust
// BAD
if { let x = get(); x > 0 } { }

// GOOD
let x = get();
if x > 0 { }
