let b = Arc::clone(&a);
```

## cmp_null

Comparing to null pointer.

```rust
// BAD
if ptr == std::ptr::null() { }

// GOOD
if ptr.is_null() { }
```

## collapsible_if

Nested if can be combined.

```rust
