```

## explicit_iter_loop

Explicit iter() in for loop.

```rust
// BAD
for x in vec.iter() { }
for x in vec.iter_mut() { }

// GOOD
for x in &vec { }
for x in &mut vec { }
```

## field_reassign_with_default

Reassigning default fields.

```rust
