```

## excessive_nesting

Too much nesting.

```rust
// BAD
fn foo() {
    if a {
        if b {
            for x in items {
                if c {
                    match d {
                        // ...
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

// GOOD - extract functions, use early returns
